{"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(_:isOn:extraLabel:description:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(_:tableName:bundle:isOn:extraLabel:description:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(isOn:label:extraLabel:description:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations","generated":true}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"macOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"16.0","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"11.0","deprecated":false}],"title":"OUDSRadioItem","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents13OUDSRadioItemV","roleHeading":"Structure","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Layouts","anchor":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}]},{"text":": like the ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"text":" layout but with a trailing radio indicator and a leading optional decorative icon","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The radio indicator has two available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is filled with a filled circle, the user has made the action to select the radio"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is empty, does not contain anything, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the radio"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The radio can be also outlined in some cases.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and optional texts and a custom radio trait."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"text":"can be used outside a dedicated picker, thus it does not need any tag and associated type.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection)","","    \/\/ Localizable from bundle can also be used","    OUDSRadioItem(LocalizedStringKey(\"option_label\"), bundle: Bundle.module, isOn: $selection)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, and an additional label but without text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection, extraLabel: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection, extraLabel: \"The Beatles\", description: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing radio with a label, a description, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                  isOn: $selection,","                  description: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                  isReversed: true,","                  isError: true,","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                  isOn: $selection,","                  isError: true,","                  errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $selection)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related radio as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $selection, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $selection, isReadOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to flip your icon depending to the layout direction or not (e.g. if RTL mode lose semantics  \/ meanings):","type":"text"}]},{"code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Cocorico !\",","                  isOn: $selection,","                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering"},{"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_OrangeCompact"}]},{"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_Wireframe"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"name":"Version","type":"aside","style":"note"},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Radio button item is a UI element that allows to select a single option from a set of mutually exclusive choices.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Radio button item covers a wider range of contexts by allowing to toggle the visibility of additional text labels and icon assets.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem"]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSRadioItem/body":{"title":"body","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/body","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem\/body","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"body","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSRadioItem":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Radio button item is a UI element that allows to select a single option from a set of mutually exclusive choices."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Radio button item covers a wider range of contexts by allowing to toggle the visibility of additional text labels and icon assets."}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSRadioItem","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},"component_radioItem_Orange":{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Orange","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_radioItem_Orange.png"}],"type":"image","alt":"A radio item component in light and dark modes with Orange theme"},"component_radioItem_OrangeCompact":{"identifier":"component_radioItem_OrangeCompact","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_radioItem_OrangeCompact.png"}],"type":"image","alt":"A radio item component in light and dark modes with Orange Compact theme"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSRadioItem/View-Implementations":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem\/view-implementations","title":"View Implementations","kind":"article","abstract":[],"role":"collectionGroup","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s8SendableP":{"title":"Swift.Sendable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSRadioPicker":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioPicker","abstract":[{"text":"A picker allowing to expose several radio buttons and choose only one within the others.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Each radio button contains a “tag”, i.e. a supposed to be unique value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker will expose the choosen value through this “ta